data.message:
Holy Shit! 16 years? 😮 Been listening to MMLP every day recently. I'm not sure if it's true if Eminem/You have Aspergers or not... but I've recently been told that I have it. Which explains a lot 😂😂 
I for one am actually happy with it and glad to be able to "figure myself out". 
I used to be a singer... gave up thanks to bullies but gonna try again! Thank you for your kick ass raps. Life would be empty Without You haha!
